videos.description: D'Shawn Schwartz feeds Lucas Siewert, who lines up and sinks a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Siewert knocks down 3 for Colorado) 2020/02/13

videos.headline: Siewert knocks down 3 for Colorado

videos.description: McKinley Wright IV tosses an alley-oop lob to Tyler Bey, who catches it and puts it in for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Bey knocks in nice alley-oop layup) 2020/02/13

videos.headline: Bey knocks in nice alley-oop layup

videos.description: Oregon's Chandler Lawson steals the ball, and drives to the basket for a layup at the other end while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Lawson's steal leads to and-1 layup) 2020/02/13

videos.headline: Lawson's steal leads to and-1 layup

videos.description: Oregon uses good ball movement and gets it to Payton Pritchard, who hits a 3-pointer with four seconds left on the shot clock.
videos.headline: Pritchard knocks in deep 3

videos.description: D'Shawn Schwartz squares up and hits a stepback 3-pointer for Colorado.
videos.headline: Schwartz nails corner 3
